					<description><![CDATA[Hello,

I am a registered music therapist from New Zealand. I would suggest the author do a through literature search on music therapy as most the research questions asked have already been answered in music therapy research.

The music therapy Cochrane Reviews are a good place to start:
http://www.cochrane.org/search/reviews/music%20therapy]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello,</p>
<p>I am a registered music therapist from New Zealand. I would suggest the author do a through literature search on music therapy as most the research questions asked have already been answered in music therapy research.</p>
<p>The music therapy Cochrane Reviews are a good place to start:<br />
<a href="http://www.cochrane.org/search/reviews/music%20therapy" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.cochrane.org/search/reviews/music%20therapy</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
