					<description><![CDATA[After all, what is said on the subject of &#039;music therapy&#039; -- either listening to it or participating in a music programme, it cannot be disputed that music, heals and calms the mind and in turn, accelerates recovery from health issues. Most of us are fond of music, in some form or other and do we not attend to music performances which gives us pleasure, is it not? Pleasure and in turn, happiness promotes health.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>After all, what is said on the subject of &#8216;music therapy&#8217; &#8212; either listening to it or participating in a music programme, it cannot be disputed that music, heals and calms the mind and in turn, accelerates recovery from health issues. Most of us are fond of music, in some form or other and do we not attend to music performances which gives us pleasure, is it not? Pleasure and in turn, happiness promotes health.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
